		{"id":"4196f94c5b8b6996","type":"text","text":"# 【中山家电】热烈祝贺广东惠利普智能科技股份有限公司加入协会！\n\n惠利普的情况\n\n _2024年08月07日 17:40_ _广东_\n\n![图片](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/bL2iaicTYdZn69jD1O26uac4ncb0jtQQRVf2QNBlPc14hd6EOGUwzPX7tnVO0Zvc56CXHOCGxqic7WRE47GjIPiaxQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&wxfrom=13&tp=wxpic)\n\n**热****烈祝贺**\n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n广东惠利普智能科技\n\n股份有限公司\n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n**加    入**\n\n**中山市家用电器行业协会**\n\n  \n\n**副会长单位**\n\n  \n\n**_01_**\n\n  \n\n**企业简介**\n\n  \n\n  \n\n![](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ksxsfPFR5bGW5gTr0iaHt7oDtA10CHEXE4XgASYqeHB7EbMC6SH6mw4PO5LkB0MnvP4wEeK2TaacjuQWIT5gPCw/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg&wxfrom=13&tp=wxpic)\n\n![图片](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/Ljib4So7yuWhfia9on4fZo5v4lUjy2oZ6xHsBqLzb4IicTGdYwQNiatglE2AG7auYFE7UWlGsgRnWs2DqZf7ge7JNw/640?wx_fmt=gif&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1)\n\n**01**\n\n广东惠利普智能科技股份有限公司始于1992年，是一家专业从事步进电机、直流无刷电机、伺服电机及变频驱动控制系统的研发、生产、销售于一体的高科技企业。公司下设一个技术研究院、六个子分公司、三个生产基地，现有的10多条生产线，一年能生产1亿台电机。\n\n![图片](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ksxsfPFR5bGW5gTr0iaHt7oDtA10CHEXEkEWnIBZiaVoB7VnribVWESceUpAePOUuPZ4UsHtXBu706tXJa1lcicibwA/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)\n\n  \n\n![图片](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ksxsfPFR5bGW5gTr0iaHt7oDtA10CHEXEXHMBFOfiasUY3JsFDYiaicJwB1pGhEGdkB0dicUoIRrswZgaNl4wDBvCPA/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)\n\n  \n\n![图片](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ksxsfPFR5bGW5gTr0iaHt7oDtA10CHEXE60vkhoRK8K47aLm7bNeexf3JbgicVod014Jat2ObDL8ceDVQ2QPRZMw/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)\n\n  \n\n**_02_**\n\n  \n\n**企业实力**\n\n  \n\n  \n\n30年来，惠利普积累专利近200项，业务覆盖模具研发制造、定转子高速精密冲压、精密机壳拉伸冲压、压铸、注塑、自动化设备，上下游产业链齐全，是国家专精特新小巨人企业、国家高新技术企业、 广东省专精特新企业。\n\n![图片](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ksxsfPFR5bGW5gTr0iaHt7oDtA10CHEXEgUAX5fRvMBGH2fu88UCYI4N3oUGU1gMYA0ibLWgL5NnyTf3jMEQpHnQ/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)\n\n  \n\n![图片](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ksxsfPFR5bGW5gTr0iaHt7oDtA10CHEXEkZ2TicfzsY1YM76T28t3pSIac29jwE7zIMoRHW4kxqGwA74m8NA26gg/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)\n\n  \n\n![图片](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ksxsfPFR5bGW5gTr0iaHt7oDtA10CHEXEV7oQrE6iaeSYqNibDPgxIWY8KUFPIlPBA1GCSZuc9keLC4oUvqIfuWuA/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)\n\n  \n\n![图片](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ksxsfPFR5bGW5gTr0iaHt7oDtA10CHEXEEiaibZQCamibicFHMG8jbVvJYV62LK6qWBx3Bn8gGpRc99jia74lp75yVPg/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)\n\n  \n\n![图片](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ksxsfPFR5bGW5gTr0iaHt7oDtA10CHEXEuNhwiajMtAHNaicENRicYEmBATnUh6JGT7LyHe0pydXkWescRjkDIUVtA/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)\n\n  \n\n![图片](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ksxsfPFR5bGW5gTr0iaHt7oDtA10CHEXEicQQ2KiabaGwj2AGxlPoDhrib5W4UthAPwnJI2lrLXvk5ibgibHVqgTRdvQ/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)\n\n  \n\n![图片](https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ksxsfPFR5bGW5gTr0iaHt7oDtA10CHEXEib8Ik3ERerWXMrgbQcWCWiaTicibE0hd5VnbDO0xsGMmZichyjSxd0hicIUg/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1)\n\n  \n\n![图片](data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'%3F%3E%3Csvg width='1px' height='1px' viewBox='0 0 1 1' version='1.1' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3E%3Ctitle%3E%3C/title%3E%3Cg stroke='none' stroke-width='1' fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd' fill-opacity='0'%3E%3Cg transform='translate(-249.000000, -126.000000)' fill='%23FFFFFF'%3E%3Crect x='249' y='126' width='1' height='1'%3E%3C/rect%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E)\n\n  \n\n![图片](data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'%3F%3E%3Csvg width='1px' height='1px' viewBox='0 0 1 1' version='1.1' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3E%3Ctitle%3E%3C/title%3E%3Cg stroke='none' stroke-width='1' fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd' fill-opacity='0'%3E%3Cg transform='translate(-249.000000, -126.000000)' fill='%23FFFFFF'%3E%3Crect x='249' y='126' width='1' height='1'%3E%3C/rect%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E)\n\n  \n\n![图片](data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'%3F%3E%3Csvg width='1px' height='1px' viewBox='0 0 1 1' version='1.1' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3E%3Ctitle%3E%3C/title%3E%3Cg stroke='none' stroke-width='1' fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd' fill-opacity='0'%3E%3Cg transform='translate(-249.000000, -126.000000)' fill='%23FFFFFF'%3E%3Crect x='249' y='126' width='1' height='1'%3E%3C/rect%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E)\n\n  \n\n**_03_**\n\n  \n\n**产品服务**\n\n  \n\n  \n\n惠利普产品广泛应用于各类电风扇、空调、冰箱、空气净化器、厨电、卫浴、监控等领域，并能为客户提供变频控制驱动整体解决方案，所研发生产的外转子直流无刷电机、永磁同步电机、风机、推杆电机等电机产品深受市场欢迎，目前已与美的、格力、TCL、长虹、松下等头部家电品牌建立合作关系。\n\n![图片](data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'%3F%3E%3Csvg width='1px' height='1px' viewBox='0 0 1 1' version='1.1' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3E%3Ctitle%3E%3C/title%3E%3Cg stroke='none' stroke-width='1' fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd' fill-opacity='0'%3E%3Cg transform='translate(-249.000000, -126.000000)' fill='%23FFFFFF'%3E%3Crect x='249' y='126' width='1' height='1'%3E%3C/rect%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E)\n\n  \n\n![图片](data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'%3F%3E%3Csvg width='1px' height='1px' viewBox='0 0 1 1' version='1.1' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3E%3Ctitle%3E%3C/title%3E%3Cg stroke='none' stroke-width='1' fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd' fill-opacity='0'%3E%3Cg transform='translate(-249.000000, -126.000000)' fill='%23FFFFFF'%3E%3Crect x='249' y='126' width='1' height='1'%3E%3C/rect%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E)\n\n  \n\n![图片](data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'%3F%3E%3Csvg width='1px' height='1px' viewBox='0 0 1 1' version='1.1' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3E%3Ct